text: Rebecca Donoghue (born 24 December 1981) is a New Zealand water polo player. She competed for the New Zealand women's national water polo team in the 2005 World Aquatics Championships, 2006 Commonwealth Games, and 2007 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * maranuis-rebecca- donoghue Getty * russias-sofya-konukh-is-smothered Getty Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:New Zealand water polo players
